{"tid":1718070,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［戰術po]唔知之後果幾日要做咩請你入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-11-13T18:13:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T18:21:33.000Z","uid":159228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3c30106c22411837cd9ecba61f660fc583259757","tid":1718070,"uid":159228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T18:13:16.000Z","msg":"各大學守緊嘅手足，請你地要不斷將防線推前，令更多地方納入你哋嘅領地範圍，每一間大學都要咁做<br />\n<br />\n趁而家班狗傾緊點對付你地就係最好時機，佔領更多嘅道路，令交通癱瘓，令更多地方納入我地嘅範圍。班狗一分散搞大學，其他區馬上開花，搞ifc，搞機場，搞狗竇。<br />\n<br />\n從來我哋嘅優勢都係人多，黑狗無可能同時顧曬每一間大學，十八區同埋每個春袋，必須令到香港無限期三罷。區區咁搞法popo好快就會彈盡糧絕，香港人將會嚟一口六月至今最大嘅反咬<br />\n<br />\n咁loop落去我地一撚定會嬴！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n香港人，還拖<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下面係作戰討論區，歡迎手足提供更多意見"},{"pid":"b8f947b108dec50bc909638e6ab18762076ddcd3","tid":1718070,"uid":159228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T18:13:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9b434e8b2b8f505ec47442fa327d186c1ed3f3d5","tid":1718070,"uid":159228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T18:14:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"05db84724bd079570e868239e41fc45c96b95549","tid":1718070,"uid":159228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T18:14:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a00da09ac3ea179c640126192c65ee48f1359e4","tid":1718070,"uid":159228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T18:14:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"717a40a627728369cb9507f6152364fd24969235","tid":1718070,"uid":159228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T18:14:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cd749b59e0908da71120d46351a845bbb1be039f","tid":1718070,"uid":159228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc